snippet.title: OMORI Preorder Promo
snippet.description:
OMOCAT's critically-acclaimed video game, OMORI, is up for physical preorder for Nintendo Switch™ and PlayStation® 4.

OMOCAT: https://www.omocat-shop.com/ 
Fangamer: https://www.fangamer.com/

Explore a strange world full of colorful friends and foes. Navigate through the vibrant and the mundane in order to uncover a forgotten past.

When the time comes, the path you’ve chosen will determine your fate... and perhaps the fate of others as well.

--Credits--
Trailer: Everdraed
Music: bansheebeat (Original Compositions by Jami Carignan and Pedro Silva)
Illustration: OMOCAT, LLC.
Director: OMOCAT
OMORI is ported by MP2 Games
